full_title: MotorSport by Migos, Nicki Minaj & Cardi B
title: MotorSport

description.plain:
On “MotorSport,” Takeoff, Quavo and Offset rap about their riches, while Cardi and Nicki take aim at their competition. It’s the lead single off Culture II, the highly anticipated sequel to 2017’s Culture.

The track was produced by CuBeatz and Murda Beatz, who are both frequent collaborators with the Migos, having produced past hits like “Get Right Witcha” and “Pipe It Up.”

The music video was released on December 7, 2017, and an earlier version of the song with a slightly different verse from Nicki Minaj was played by DJ Akademiks on April 12, 2018.
